===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|Scotland||Ireland", later also "Scotland|lit=land of the Scots}}, equivalent to {{compound|Scot|land|lang=en|nocat=1}}. Based on the Latin word {{m|la|Scōtus||Gael}}.

